  "description": {
   "en": "Akari is a closet otaku of 2.5 dimensional idols.  \n  \nOne of the things she looks forward to in life is her otaku activities with Onda, a fellow 2.5D idol otaku who looks scary but at heart, is actually like a maiden who is madly in love when it comes to his favourite idol.  \n  \nThey go to viewing events, handshake events, collaboration cafes and also collect trading goods together.  \n  \nHe's a close male otaku friend who she enjoys sharing interests with but who would have thought that Onda would one day confess his love for her?!"
  },
